trans-unit.source: Generates types and attribute declarations from internal type mapping information for SOAP-encoded message parts defined in a WSDL document.
trans-unit.target: Genera tipi e le dichiarazioni di attributo da informazioni di mapping di tipo interno per parti di messaggio con codifica SOAP definito in un documento WSDL.

trans-unit.source: The SoapCodeExporter class is used by the [Web Services Description Language Tool (Wsdl.exe)](http://msdn.microsoft.com/en-us/b9210348-8bc2-4367-8c91-d1a04b403e88) and the <xref:System.Web.Services.Description.ServiceDescriptionImporter> class while generating client proxy classes or abstract server classes from a Web Services Description Language (WSDL) document.
trans-unit.target: La classe SoapCodeExporter viene utilizzata il [Web Services Description Language Tool (Wsdl.exe)](http://msdn.microsoft.com/en-us/b9210348-8bc2-4367-8c91-d1a04b403e88) e <xref:System.Web.Services.Description.ServiceDescriptionImporter>classe durante la generazione di classi proxy client o server astratte da un documento Web Services Description Language (WSDL).</xref:System.Web.Services.Description.ServiceDescriptionImporter>

trans-unit.source: Instead of using SoapCodeExporter directly, use Wsdl.exe.
trans-unit.target: Anziché utilizzare direttamente SoapCodeExporter, utilizzare Wsdl.exe.
